|- bgcolor=#D0E7FF\n| align=center | 18.\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} Palermo Volley\n| align=center | '''1'''\n| align=center | \n| 1998\u201399\n|- bgcolor=#F5FAFF\n| align=center | 19.\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Roma Volley]]\n| align=center | '''1'''\n| align=center | \n| 1999\u201300\n|- bgcolor=#D0E7FF\n| align=center | 20.\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Umbria Volley|Perugia Volley]]\n| align=center | '''1'''\n| align=center |\n| [[2009\u201310 CEV Challenge Cup|2009\u201310]] \n|- bgcolor=#F5FAFF\n| align=center | 21.\n| {{flagicon|POL}} [[AZS Cz\u0119stochowa]]\n| align=center | '''1'''\n| align=center | \n| [[2011\u201312 CEV Challenge Cup|2011\u201312]]\n|- bgcolor=#D0E7FF\n| align=center | 22.\n| {{flagicon|TUR}} [[Fenerbah\u00e7e Men's Volleyball|Fenerbah\u00e7e Grundig]]\n| align=center | '''1'''\n| align=center | \n| [[2013\u201314 CEV Challenge Cup|2013\u201314]]\n|- bgcolor=#F5FAFF\n| align=center | 23.\n| {{flagicon|SRB}} [[OK Vojvodina|Vojvodina]]\n| align=center | '''1'''\n| align=center | \n| [[2014\u201315 CEV Challenge Cup|2014\u201315]]\n|- bgcolor=#D0E7FF\n| align=center | 24.\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[BluVolley Verona|Calzedonia Verona]]\n| align=center | '''1'''\n| align=center | \n| [[2015\u201316 CEV Challenge Cup|2015\u201316]]\n|- bgcolor=#F5FAFF\n| align=center | 25.\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[G.S. Porto Robur Costa|Bunge Ravenna]]\n| align=center | '''1'''\n| align=center |\n| [[2017\u201318 CEV Challenge Cup|2017\u201318]]\n|- bgcolor=#D0E7FF\n| align=center | 26.\n| {{flagicon|YUG}} [[OK Partizan|Partizan]]\n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''2'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#F5FAFF\n| align=center | 27.\n| {{flagicon|BEL}} [[Knack Roeselare]]\n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''2'''\n|\n|- bgcolor=#D0E7FF\n| align=center | 28.\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} Amare pi\u00f9 Loreto \n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#F5FAFF\n| align=center | 29.\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} Toseroni Roma \n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#D0E7FF\n| align=center | 30.\n| {{flagicon|NED}} Orion Doetinchem \n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#F5FAFF\n| align=center | 31.\n| {{flagicon|YUG}} [[OK Bosna|Bosna]]\n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#D0E7FF\n| align=center | 32.\n| {{flagicon|URS}} [[VC Radiotechnik|Elektrotechnika]]\n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#F5FAFF\n| align=center | 33.\n| {{flagicon|RUS}} Samotlor\n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#D0E7FF\n| align=center | 34.\n| {{flagicon|GRC}} [[A.C. Orestias|AC Orestiada]]\n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#F5FAFF\n| align=center | 35.\n| {{flagicon|TUR}} Neta\u015f Istanbul \n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#D0E7FF\n| align=center | 36.\n| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[CV P\u00f2rtol]]\n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#F5FAFF\n| align=center | 37.\n| {{flagicon|RUS}} [[VC Iskra Odintsovo|Iskra Odintsovo]]\n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#D0E7FF\n| align=center | 38.\n| {{flagicon|RUS}} Lokomotiv Izoumroud \n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#F5FAFF\n| align=center | 39.\n| {{flagicon|POL}} [[Jastrz\u0119bski W\u0119giel]]\n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#D0E7FF\n| align=center | 40.\n| {{flagicon|CRO}} [[HAOK Mladost|Mladost]]\n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#F5FAFF\n| align=center | 41.\n| {{flagicon|POL}} [[AZS Politechnika Warszawska]]\n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#D0E7FF\n| align=center | 42.\n| {{flagicon|RUS}} [[Ural Ufa]]\n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#F5FAFF\n| align=center | 43.\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Top Volley Latina|Andreoli Latina]] \n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#D0E7FF\n| align=center | 44.\n| {{flagicon|POR}} [[S.L. Benfica (volleyball)|Benfica]]\n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#F5FAFF\n| align=center | 45.\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} Chaumont VB 52 \n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#D0E7FF\n| align=center | 46.\n| {{flagicon|GRC}} [[Olympiacos S.C.|Olympiacos]] \n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|- bgcolor=#F5FAFF\n| align=center | 47.\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Vero Volley Monza]]\n| align=center | \n| align=center | '''1'''\n| \n|}\n\n==Titles by country==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! Rank\n! Country\n! Won\n! Runner-up\n! Total\n|-\n| 1 ||align=left| {{ITA}} || 27 || 16 || 43\n|-\n| 2 ||align=left| {{RUS}} || 3 || 6 || 9\n|-\n| 3 ||align=left| {{TUR}} || 2 || 2 || 4 \n|-\n| 4 ||align=left| {{URS}} || 2 || 1 || 3 \n|-\n| 5 ||align=left| {{POL}} || 1 || 2 || 3 \n|-\n| 6 ||align=left| {{FRA}} || 1 || 1 || 2 \n|-\n| 7 ||align=left| {{NED}} || 1 || 1 || 2 \n|-\n|rowspan=2| 8 ||align=left| {{FRG}} || 1 || \u2013 || 1 \n|-\n|align=left| {{SRB}} || 1 || \u2013 || 1 \n|-\n| 10 ||align=left| {{YUG}} || \u2013 || 3 || 3 \n|-\n| 11 ||align=left| {{BEL}} || \u2013 || 2 || 2 \n|-\n| 12 ||align=left| {{GRC}} || \u2013 || 2 || 2 \n|-\n|rowspan=3| 13 ||align=left| {{CRO}} || \u2013 || 1 || 1\n|-\n|align=left| {{POR}} || \u2013 || 1 || 1 \n|-\n|align=left| {{ESP}} || \u2013 || 1 || 1 \n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.cev.eu CEV Website]\n*[https://www.cev.eu/Competition-Area/History.aspx?ID=1195 History of the Competition]\n\n{{CEV Challenge Cup seasons}}\n{{European Volleyball Competitions}}\n{{Professional Volleyball Leagues}}\n{{European Club Competitions}}\n{{International volleyball}}\n\n[[Category:CEV Challenge Cup| ]]\n[[Category:European men's volleyball club competitions|Challenge Cup]]\n[[Category:European volleyball records and statistics]]\n[[Category:Recurring sporting events established in 1980]]\n[[Category:1980 establishments in Europe]]\n", "name_user": "Maister1921", "label": "safe", "comment":